{
  "id": "adv_event_2401_01_01",
  "title": "にゃんか不思議なお正月！？ 1話 沙季の大掃除",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――これは、NEXT VENUSグランプリで",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "同時優勝を果たした直後の正月の出来事",
      "startTime": 2.8799999475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski001.wav",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、明けましておめでとうございます",
      "startTime": 7.2666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "明けましておめでと～！　今年もよろしくね！",
      "startTime": 11.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei001.wav",
      "text": "……あれ？　沙季ちゃん一人だけ？　他のみんなは？",
      "startTime": 17.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニピの五人はお仕事に出かけました",
      "startTime": 22.377574269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski002.wav",
      "text": "今日は夜まで帰れないそうです",
      "startTime": 25.4883222263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは実家でご家族とお正月を過ごしています",
      "startTime": 28.0442409356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski003.wav",
      "text": "今夜の年始ライブまでには戻ってくるそうです",
      "startTime": 32.2549888929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういえばすずにゃんも、元旦は",
      "startTime": 35.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei002.wav",
      "text": "親戚の集まりがあるから実家に帰るって言ってたっけ",
      "startTime": 38.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "渚ちゃんも朝早くに出かけました",
      "startTime": 42.9555337588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski004.wav",
      "text": "友達の家に遊びに行くそうです",
      "startTime": 45.9770298005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そっか……じゃあ、今日は沙季ちゃんと二人きりだね",
      "startTime": 49.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei003.wav",
      "text": "こたつに入ってお餅を食べながらゴロゴロしよう～！",
      "startTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ゴロゴロしません",
      "startTime": 59.3763727347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski005.wav",
      "text": "お正月だからって、そんな自堕落な生活は許しませんよ",
      "startTime": 61.3419501942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "という訳で、忙しくて年末に出来なかった大掃除を",
      "startTime": 65.9430394013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski006.wav",
      "text": "今から二人でやりましょう",
      "startTime": 70.2086168608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei004.wav",
      "text": "え～、芽衣はこたつでゴロゴロしたいな～",
      "startTime": 72.2763727347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一年の計は元旦にあり！　身の回りを整理整頓して",
      "startTime": 77.1346496581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski007.wav",
      "text": "清々しい気持ちで新たな一年を始めましょう！",
      "startTime": 81.9443085354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もの凄いやる気だね……",
      "startTime": 86.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei005.wav",
      "text": "……でも、そうだね。部屋が綺麗だと気持ちいいもんね",
      "startTime": 90.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei006.wav",
      "text": "芽衣も大掃除手伝うよ！",
      "startTime": 95.2685949165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとうございます。では私は廊下をお掃除するので",
      "startTime": 97.8741052308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski008.wav",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんはリビングをお願いします",
      "startTime": 102.7266162449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei007.wav",
      "text": "はーい！　頑張ってピカピカにしちゃうよ～！",
      "startTime": 105.2074385641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――小一時間後",
      "startTime": 110.8447174864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと一段落付きました",
      "startTime": 112.9113872049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski009.wav",
      "text": "建物が広いとお掃除のしがいがありますね",
      "startTime": 117.3199539503,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11970.046049699988
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "後は窓を全開にして、しばらく換気しておきましょう",
      "startTime": 120.9447205382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski010.wav",
      "text": "そう言えばリビングのお掃除はどうなったんでしょうか",
      "startTime": 126.4532872837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あははは！　この漫画面白いな～",
      "startTime": 132.844719521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei008.wav",
      "text": "続きはどこにあるんだろう？",
      "startTime": 138.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.333333300021
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……芽衣ちゃん。どうしてこたつに入って",
      "startTime": 142.1068675039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski011.wav",
      "text": "漫画を読んでいるんですか？",
      "startTime": 145.1928500177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "沙季ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 147.3402008372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei008.wav",
      "text": "この漫画の続き、どこにあるか知らない？",
      "startTime": 148.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "知りません",
      "startTime": 151.8915615239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski012.wav",
      "text": "サボってないで、ちゃんとお掃除して下さい",
      "startTime": 153.6549587888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ……そう言えばお掃除の途中だっけ",
      "startTime": 156.6582281905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei010.wav",
      "text": "ごめんごめん。面白そうな漫画を見つけて、つい……",
      "startTime": 161.3666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すぐ片付けるから。えっと、この漫画は……",
      "startTime": 166.4689968743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei011.wav",
      "text": "その辺の棚に適当に入れておけばいいよね",
      "startTime": 173.099991862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-ski013.wav",
      "text": "「適当に」……？",
      "startTime": 176.7231697557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あれ？",
      "startTime": 178.8231768765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_01-mei012.wav",
